re-to-others-using-imagery-i-like-to-go-find-a-secluded-beach-build-a-large-magnificent-sand-castle-and-then-walk-away-will-anyone-notice-probably-not-will-the-waves-eventually-destroy-it-yep-did-i-still-get-immense-satisfaction-absolutely":{"type":"header","text":"I've often described my motivation for building software to others using imagery: I like to go find a secluded beach, build a large, magnificent sand castle, and then walk away. Will anyone notice? Probably not. Will the waves eventually destroy it? Yep. Did I still get immense satisfaction? Absolutely.","value":"ive-often-described-my-motivation-for-building-software-to-others-using-imagery-i-like-to-go-find-a-secluded-beach-build-a-large-magnificent-sand-castle-and-then-walk-away-will-anyone-notice-probably-not-will-the-waves-eventually-destroy-it-yep-did-i-still-get-immense-satisfaction-absolutely","line":28,"column":0,"depth":3},"the-texture-the-juiciness-the-complexity-of-the-flavor-the-imperfections-the-joy-of-finding-a-particularly-good-one-the-cosmic-horror-of-eating-a-wormy-one-the-nostalgia-of-having-your-grandmas-strawberry-jam-with-dozens-of-individually-unique-strawberries-in-it":{"type":"header","text":"The texture, the juiciness, the complexity of the flavor, the imperfections, the joy of finding a particularly good one, the cosmic horror of eating a wormy one, the nostalgia of having your grandma's strawberry jam with dozens of individually unique strawberries in it.","value":"the-texture-the-juiciness-the-complexity-of-the-flavor-the-imperfections-the-joy-of-finding-a-particularly-good-one-the-cosmic-horror-of-eating-a-wormy-one-the-nostalgia-of-having-your-grandmas-strawberry-jam-with-dozens-of-individually-unique-strawberries-in-it","line":32,"column":0,"depth":3},"simplicity-even-if-it-sacrifices-some-ideal-functionality-has-better-survival-characteristics-than-the-right-thing":{"type":"header","text":"Simplicity, even if it sacrifices some ideal functionality has better survival characteristics than the-right-thing.","value":"simplicity-even-if-it-sacrifices-some-ideal-functionality-has-better-survival-characteristics-than-the-right-thing","line":36,"column":0,"depth":3},"roberto-blake-was-talking-about-making-100-crappy-videos-to-get-better-over-time":{"type":"header","text":"Roberto Blake was talking about making 100 crappy videos to get better over time.","value":"roberto-blake-was-talking-about-making-100-crappy-videos-to-get-better-over-time","line":40,"column":0,"depth":3},"make-the-difficult-habitual-the-habitual-easy-and-the-easy-beautiful":{"type":"header","text":"Make the difficult habitual, the habitual easy, and the easy beautiful.","value":"make-the-difficult-habitual-the-habitual-easy-and-the-easy-beautiful","line":48,"column":0,"depth":3},"a-good-match-is-a-structured-dance-where-players-aim-to-score-while-they-are-following-well-defined-rules-this-freedom-within-a-structure-is-what-makes-it-fun":{"type":"header","text":"A good match is a structured dance, where players aim to score while they are following well-defined rules. This freedom within a structure is what makes it fun.","value":"a-good-match-is-a-structured-dance-where-players-aim-to-score-while-they-are-following-well-defined-rules-this-freedom-within-a-structure-is-what-makes-it-fun","line":52,"column":0,"depth":3},"pivot-points":{"type":"header","text":"Pivot Points","value":"pivot-points","line":56,"column":0,"depth":3},"hedged-bets":{"type":"header","text":"Hedged Bets","value":"hedged-bets","line":61,"column":0,"depth":3},"motivation-often-comes-after-starting-not-before-action-produces-momentum":{"type":"header","text":"“Motivation often comes after starting, not before. Action produces momentum.”","value":"motivation-often-comes-after-starting-not-before-action-produces-momentum","line":65,"column":0,"depth":3},"focus-is-more-about-not-keeping-busy-when-you-need-to-wait-for-something":{"type":"header","text":"Focus is more about not keeping busy when you need to wait for something.","value":"focus-is-more-about-not-keeping-busy-when-you-need-to-wait-for-something","line":69,"column":0,"depth":3},"4-minutes-run-hard-enough-to-push-heart-rate-to-90-3-minutes-recover-repeat-4-times":{"type":"header","text":"4 minutes run hard enough to push heart rate to 90%, 3 minutes recover, repeat 4 times","value":"4-minutes-run-hard-enough-to-push-heart-rate-to-90-3-minutes-recover-repeat-4-times","line":73,"column":0,"depth":3},"recommended-routine---bodyweightfitness---i-dont-have-this-much-time":{"type":"header","text":"recommended routine - bodyweightfitness - I Don't Have This Much Time!","value":"recommended-routine---bodyweightfitness---i-dont-have-this-much-time","line":78,"column":0,"depth":3},"도무지-읽히지-않는-책-앞에서-내가-택한-방법은-펼쳐진-페이지-앞에서-멍때리기이다":{"type":"header","text":"도무지 읽히지 않는 책 앞에서 내가 택한 방법은 펼쳐진 페이지 앞에서 멍때리기이다.","value":"도무지-읽히지-않는-책-앞에서-내가-택한-방법은-펼쳐진-페이지-앞에서-멍때리기이다","line":82,"column":0,"depth":3},"i-think-it-should-be-everyones-primary-focus-to-sleep-well-drink-water-get-outside-get-active-and-eat-generally-decently-i-hate-to-say-it-but-if-youre-not-eating-a-good-amount-of-vegetables-and-fruit-decent-protein-sleep-etc-no-amount-of-xyz-will-catch-up-to-that-detriment":{"type":"header","text":"I think it should be everyone's primary focus to sleep well, drink water, get outside, get active, and eat generally decently. I hate to say it, but if you're not eating a good amount of vegetables and fruit, decent protein, sleep, etc, no amount of XYZ will catch up to that detriment.","value":"i-think-it-should-be-everyones-primary-focus-to-sleep-well-drink-water-get-outside-get-active-and-eat-generally-decently-i-hate-to-say-it-but-if-youre-not-eating-a-good-amount-of-vegetables-and-fruit-decent-protein-sleep-etc-no-amount-of-xyz-will-catch-up-to-that-detriment","line":87,"column":0,"depth":3},"my-real-battle-is-doing-good-versus-doing-nothing":{"type":"header","text":"My real battle is doing good versus doing nothing.","value":"my-real